data.text: @Brianpannell11 & they have been testing these for awhile & they have not been able to once get it approved! Ya know I still don’t trust FDA, so I wouldn’t be surprised if they get paid off to approve it eventually.

@AbigailJoyFloat And we're the test subjects! Not even FDA approved yet, only authorized as emergency status. Testing for these things can take up to 10 years to be FDA approved. No thanks, I'm not a lab rat!
